{"tid":1369930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，呢個香港越黎越精彩","createTime":"2019-07-26T23:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T00:09:09.000Z","uid":242805,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"258c2de0b6d4e2266e389de835de68538340a400","tid":1369930,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:00:54.000Z","msg":"屌那媽，政府有無數次解決既機會，但係因為垃圾官員同豬隊友所以搞到咁，真係世界上第二廢既政府。<br />\n<br />\n依家連黑警都叮一聲醒撚埋，真係睇你點死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好，元朗之行要小心，加油。<br />\n<br />\n帶野保護自己，例如攝影師一定要帶支最撚硬既腳架<br />\n<br />\n最緊要小心小心小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日要直踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陪唔到你地<br />\n<br />\n但係，祝香港人成功，祝香港和平🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰"},{"pid":"f9354287ef773b60e50479ac6d8eac61c171850d","tid":1369930,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:12:56.000Z","msg":"萬事小心<br />\n勿落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81cb826c80e6c0a1a70f08e3a22416f6f7e3c4f","tid":1369930,"uid":242805,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9354287ef773b60e50479ac6d8eac61c171850d","tid":1369930,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:12:56.000Z","msg":"萬事小心<br />\n勿落單<img src=\"/assets/faces